{"tid":990803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"年關近  中国大媽湧入香港　搶貨搶位起飛腳兜巴星","createTime":"2019-01-22T01:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T03:16:28.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ab42383092db2651fb3b0f221662a0c4cda43ec5","tid":990803,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:46:59.000Z","msg":"中國大媽近日大舉入侵香港辦年貨，瘋狂搶購化妝品、奶粉、零食及日常用品，還與當地民眾起衝突，惹得議員發聲要抵制惡大媽。<br />\n<br />\n今日出版的《自由時報》報導，中國「水貨客」近來湧進香港，尤其是新界北區搶購評貨，當街開箱留下大量垃圾，又不亂闖馬路、當眾如廁等行為使交通大亂，甚至在港鐵搶位。<br />\n<br />\n據悉在「羅湖站」，１名大媽搶位被指責，飆罵「去你╳的」、「你敢弄我」、「我讓中國政府弄你」，最後竟出手掌摑並踢踹一名男乘客。香港鐵路公司應成立「惡大媽應變部隊」，保障港人搭乘地鐵的權益。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190122/1504965\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190122%2F1504965&d=SEj7soRn3n8iCTLNY85HXjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=ab3bc3c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190122%2F1504965&h=8caeb17c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190122/1504965</a>"},{"pid":"46e7d6cf9a20c73d886576d2783866fbb40d6819","tid":990803,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T03:16:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}